{
  "info": {
    "name": "Services AI App",
    "_postman_id": "services-ai-app-collection",
    "schema": "https://schema.getpostman.com/json/collection/v2.1.0/collection.json",
    "description": "Full API testing collection for Services AI App"
  },
  "variable": [
    { "key": "baseUrl", "value": "http://localhost:8000" },
    { "key": "customerToken", "value": "" },
    { "key": "providerToken", "value": "" },
    { "key": "bookingId", "value": "" }
  ],
  "item": [
    {
      "name": "1. Auth",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "Customer Signup",
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "exec": [
                  "const res = pm.response.json();",
                  "if (res.token) pm.collectionVariables.set('customerToken', res.token);"
                ]
              }
            }
          ],
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "url": "{{baseUrl}}/api/auth/signup",
            "header": [{ "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"email\": \"customer@test.com\",\n  \"password\": \"test1234\",\n  \"firstName\": \"Ali\",\n  \"lastName\": \"Raza\",\n  \"role\": \"CUSTOMER\",\n  \"location\": {\n    \"address\": \"F-8, Islamabad\",\n    \"city\": \"Islamabad\",\n    \"geo\": {\n      \"type\": \"Point\",\n      \"coordinates\": [73.0715, 33.7141]\n    }\n  }\n}"
            }
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Customer Login",
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "exec": [
                  "const res = pm.response.json();",
                  "if (res.token) pm.collectionVariables.set('customerToken', res.token);"
                ]
              }
            }
          ],
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "url": "{{baseUrl}}/api/auth/login",
            "header": [{ "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"email\": \"customer@test.com\",\n  \"password\": \"test1234\"\n}"
            }
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Provider Login (Seeded)",
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "exec": [
                  "const res = pm.response.json();",
                  "if (res.token) pm.collectionVariables.set('providerToken', res.token);"
                ]
              }
            }
          ],
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "url": "{{baseUrl}}/api/auth/login",
            "header": [{ "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"email\": \"ahmed.khan@provider.com\",\n  \"password\": \"provider123\"\n}"
            }
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Get Profile (Customer)",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "url": "{{baseUrl}}/api/auth/me",
            "header": [{ "key": "Authorization", "value": "Bearer {{customerToken}}" }]
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Get Profile (Provider)",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "url": "{{baseUrl}}/api/auth/me",
            "header": [{ "key": "Authorization", "value": "Bearer {{providerToken}}" }]
          }
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "name": "2. Bookings — Customer",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "List My Bookings",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "url": "{{baseUrl}}/api/bookings",
            "header": [{ "key": "Authorization", "value": "Bearer {{customerToken}}" }]
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "List Bookings (by status)",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/api/bookings?status=COMPLETED",
              "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
              "path": ["api", "bookings"],
              "query": [{ "key": "status", "value": "COMPLETED" }]
            },
            "header": [{ "key": "Authorization", "value": "Bearer {{customerToken}}" }]
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Get Booking Details",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "url": "{{baseUrl}}/api/bookings/{{bookingId}}",
            "header": [{ "key": "Authorization", "value": "Bearer {{customerToken}}" }]
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Pay for Booking",
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "url": "{{baseUrl}}/api/bookings/{{bookingId}}/pay",
            "header": [{ "key": "Authorization", "value": "Bearer {{customerToken}}" }]
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Submit Review (Customer)",
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "url": "{{baseUrl}}/api/bookings/{{bookingId}}/review",
            "header": [
              { "key": "Authorization", "value": "Bearer {{customerToken}}" },
              { "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }
            ],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"rating\": 5,\n  \"comment\": \"Excellent work, very professional!\"\n}"
            }
          }
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "name": "3. Bookings — Provider",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "List Provider Bookings",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "url": "{{baseUrl}}/api/bookings",
            "header": [{ "key": "Authorization", "value": "Bearer {{providerToken}}" }]
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Get Booking Details",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "url": "{{baseUrl}}/api/bookings/{{bookingId}}",
            "header": [{ "key": "Authorization", "value": "Bearer {{providerToken}}" }]
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Initialize Booking",
          "request": {
            "method": "PATCH",
            "url": "{{baseUrl}}/api/bookings/{{bookingId}}/status",
            "header": [
              { "key": "Authorization", "value": "Bearer {{providerToken}}" },
              { "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }
            ],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"status\": \"INITIALIZED\"\n}"
            }
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Mark as Completed",
          "request": {
            "method": "PATCH",
            "url": "{{baseUrl}}/api/bookings/{{bookingId}}/status",
            "header": [
              { "key": "Authorization", "value": "Bearer {{providerToken}}" },
              { "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }
            ],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"status\": \"PROVIDER_COMPLETED\"\n}"
            }
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Cancel Booking",
          "request": {
            "method": "PATCH",
            "url": "{{baseUrl}}/api/bookings/{{bookingId}}/status",
            "header": [
              { "key": "Authorization", "value": "Bearer {{providerToken}}" },
              { "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }
            ],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"status\": \"CANCELLED\"\n}"
            }
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Submit Review (Provider)",
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "url": "{{baseUrl}}/api/bookings/{{bookingId}}/review",
            "header": [
              { "key": "Authorization", "value": "Bearer {{providerToken}}" },
              { "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }
            ],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"rating\": 4,\n  \"comment\": \"Good customer, clear instructions\"\n}"
            }
          }
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "name": "4. Notifications",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "Get Notifications (Customer)",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "url": "{{baseUrl}}/api/bookings/notifications/list",
            "header": [{ "key": "Authorization", "value": "Bearer {{customerToken}}" }]
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Get Notifications (Provider)",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "url": "{{baseUrl}}/api/bookings/notifications/list",
            "header": [{ "key": "Authorization", "value": "Bearer {{providerToken}}" }]
          }
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "name": "5. WebSocket (Socket.IO)",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "⚡ READ ME — WebSocket Setup",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "url": "{{baseUrl}}/api",
            "description": "WebSocket testing requires Postman's Socket.IO tab:\n\n1. New > Socket.IO Request\n2. URL: http://localhost:8000/chat\n\nAUTH (pick one):\n  Option A — Headers tab: Add header 'Authorization' = 'Bearer <customerToken>'\n  Option B — Query param: Change URL to http://localhost:8000/chat?token=<customerToken>\n\n3. Click Connect\n4. You should receive a 'chat_history' event\n\n--- EVENTS TO EMIT ---\n\nEmit 'send_message':\n{ \"content\": \"I need my AC repaired\" }\n\nEmit 'action_response' to select provider:\n{ \"actionType\": \"SELECT_PROVIDER\", \"data\": { \"providerId\": \"<id>\" } }\n\nEmit 'action_response' to pay:\n{ \"actionType\": \"PAY\", \"data\": { \"bookingId\": \"<id>\" } }\n\nEmit 'action_response' to confirm:\n{ \"actionType\": \"CONFIRM_COMPLETION\", \"data\": { \"bookingId\": \"<id>\", \"confirmed\": true } }\n\nEmit 'action_response' to review:\n{ \"actionType\": \"SUBMIT_REVIEW\", \"data\": { \"rating\": 5, \"comment\": \"Great!\" } }\n\n--- EVENTS TO LISTEN FOR ---\nthinking, ai_thinking, stream, message_complete, chat_history, error"
          }
        }
      ]
    }
  ]
}
